{"lemma":"زَبَدُ","slug":"زَبَدُ","root":"ز.ب.د","root_slug":"ز-ب-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ب-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زَبَد","root":"زبد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":7,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":13},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17354","n17355","n17356"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to feed (someone) butter"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to churn (milk)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give (someone) a gift"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make creamy"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to add cream to something"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause to foam"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"butter"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cinder"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"foam"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"scum"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"liquid"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَبَدَ (zabada) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of زُبْدَة (zubda)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17354","headword_ar":"زَبْدٌ","root":"zbd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[originally an inf. n.,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gift."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, Msb.) So in the saying (S, TA) of Mo- hammad, (TA,) mentioned in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~aA laA naqobalu","text_ar":"اـِنَّا لَا نَقْبَلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaboda Almu$orikiyna","text_ar":"زَبْدَ المُشْرِكِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily we will not accept the gift of the believers in a plurality of Gods"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahaY Eano zabodi Almu$orikiyna","text_ar":"نَهَى عَنْ زَبْدِ المُشْرِكِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  (A, Mgh, Msb) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mohammad)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forbade"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the acceptance of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gift"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the believers in a plurality of Gods"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","A","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n17355","headword_ar":"زُبْدٌ","root":"zbd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fresh butter of the cow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"buffalo"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is produced by churning from milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of cows"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"buffaloes"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats;"},{"kind":"text","text":"what is thus produced from camels' milk being termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubaAbN","text_ar":"جُبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodN","text_ar":"زُبْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubod","text_ar":"زُبْد"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samon","text_ar":"سَمْن"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before it is clarified over the fire;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"butter before it is clarified over the fire;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubod","text_ar":"زُبْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabad","text_ar":"زَبَد"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is extracted from milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zub~aAdN","text_ar":"زُبَّادٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodN","text_ar":"زُبْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodapN","text_ar":"زُبْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a more particular term, (S, M, L, Msb,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece, bit, portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubod","text_ar":"زُبْد"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodu All~abani","text_ar":"زُبْدُ اللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the froth"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragowap","text_ar":"رَغْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"[if this be not a mistake occasioned by finding"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~ubodu","text_ar":"الزُّبْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadu All~abani","text_ar":"زَبَدُ اللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodu All~abani","text_ar":"زُبْدُ اللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qado Sar~aHa AlmaHoDu Eani","text_ar":"قَدْ صَرَّحَ المَحْضُ عَنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~ubodi","text_ar":"الزُّبْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The clear milk has become distinct from the fresh butter"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a prov., relating to the appearance of the truth after information that has been doubted. (L.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Airotajanati Alz~ubodapu","text_ar":"اِرْتَجَنَتِ الزُّبْدَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is another prov. [expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjn","text_ar":"رجن"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b2-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodapN","text_ar":"زُبْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has for its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubadN","text_ar":"زُبَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is metonymically applied to (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"best, portions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or what we often term the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cream"},{"kind":"text","text":"(by which word the sing. also may be rendered) of anything; as, for instance,] of discourse, or of a story or the like. (Har p. 222, q. v.) ―         -b3-  [And it also means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An issue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"event:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaDa","text_ar":"مَخَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) generally,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is relishable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing."},{"kind":"text","text":"Hence, app.,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEumuri","text_ar":"العُمُرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna liqaAw^uka zubodapa","text_ar":"كَانَ لِقَاوُكَ زُبْدَةَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The meeting with thee was"},{"kind":"text","text":"emphatically"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the event of life;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the most relishable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing, event of life"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","K","S","M","L"]},{"entry_id":"n17356","headword_ar":"زَبَدٌ","root":"zbd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Froth, foam, spume,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scum:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) it is of water, (S, L, K,) &c.; (K;) of the sea, (A, Msb,) &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragowapN","text_ar":"رَغْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in signification"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Msb;) and of a cooking-pot; (A;) and of a camel, (S,) [i. e.] of a braying camel's mouth, (A,) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white foam"},{"kind":"text","text":"upon the lips of a camel when he is excited by lust; (TA;) and of the cud; and of spittle; (L;) and [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dross,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of silver: (S:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadapN","text_ar":"زَبَدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a more particular term [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat, thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadN","text_ar":"زَبَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azobaAdN","text_ar":"اَزْبَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxar~ama zabaduhu","text_ar":"تَخَرَّمَ زَبَدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 5 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xrm","text_ar":"خرم"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["L","S","K","A","Msb"]}]}}